PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of British Columbia of the administration and control over a parcel of vacant land situate on MOUNT LOLO, in the City of Kamloops, that contains an area of some 7.651 hectares, which is to be used as the site for communication and radar facilities (District Lot 6280, Kamloops Division, Yale District).
